Package: econiodatajp
Type: Package
Title: Ready-to-Use Japanese Input-Output Tables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mizuki", "Uchida", , "uchidamizuki@vivaldi.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ready-to-use input-output (IO) tables for Japan,
    built from data published by Japan's national government (e-Stat),
    individual prefectures, and the Research Institute of Economy, Trade
    and Industry (RIETI). Tables are archived and rebuilt on demand via
    the 'tarchives' and 'targets' packages, and returned as 'econio'
    input-output table objects for direct use with its analysis functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
